The paper discusses the use of blockchain technology for building a trustable machine learning system, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also proposes a method for training machine learning models and generating synthetic data, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the implementation of machine learning on edge devices, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE).
